main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 3392/93 is hereby amended as follows:
1. In Article 2 (1), 'categories III to VI' are replaced by 'categories III to VII';
2. In Article 4 (1) (a), 'category I' is replaced by 'categories I and VII';
3. The following is added to the Annex thereto:
'Category VII
Whole milk, untreated'.
